{"tid":1659643,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［日本戰線］jj插富士山求在日巴絲入嚟望一眼","createTime":"2019-10-17T05:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T19:41:49.000Z","uid":304288,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"52f761ad59205b4999fa0f73a86c439408145fab","tid":1659643,"uid":304288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:16:32.000Z","msg":"標題呃咗大家唔好意思，其實我連富士山都未去過的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過真心多謝你哋肯入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n在日香港人麻煩俾少少時間睇一睇，其他巴絲麻煩幫手推同share<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">（尼個post係針對日本戰線嘅，所以我唔太大力推佢上頂。但求入咗嚟嘅巴絲幫幫手幫幫腳，share個post俾你識嘅喺日本讀緊書嘅朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我收倒frd send返個post俾我為之合格標準，我一日未收返倒自己個post，我就繼續係咁推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</span><br />\n（通常去得日本讀書嗰啲都係毒撚宅男女嚟，但係即使以前無乜點同我哋傾過計都好，求各位照send 個post俾我哋尼班可憐嘅毒j<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先放返細佬之前個post出嚟俾大家睇睇先～ 利申長文，所以比較忙嘅話可以只睇最尾嘅「注意事項」就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［日本文宣/遊行］少少反省+今後策略研究<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656035</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">入正題！</span></span><br />\n今次主要係想講下小弟嚟緊打算喺日本做嘅行動，而我希望各位喺日本/有關注日本戰線嘅巴絲可以幫幫手。以下為一個小總結先：<br />\n一）統一日本（嘅香港人）<br />\n- 方便組織行動<br />\n- 跨縣溝通<br />\n二）提供、收集&amp;整理在日行動資訊<br />\n- 在日行動&amp;文宣紀錄；<br />\n- 日本人為我哋做過嘅行動等<br />\n三）記者訪問同同議員溝通時借用名義(後面詳述)<br />\n<br />\n相信大家都會因爲唔知我係邊個而有所顧忌。我當然亦都唔會直接公開自己身分，但為咗提高大家嘅信任度，我喺度放三條線出嚟俾你哋有需要時起我㡳。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 我喺日本行動嘅個人名義係 K(日文 けいフォン)<br />\n- 我係11/10東京大學，沈旭暉個talk之後出嚟講野嗰兩個香港人學生入面嘅其中一個<br />\n- 我係九月尾喺東京ICU(日本現任兩位公主讀嗰間大學)個Asian Studies Week: Learn about Hong Kong，為期9日活動嘅主搞手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNHZKs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNHZKs.png&h=40e8ddf4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TkpfAhS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTkpfAhS.png&h=2efffb35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">一）統一日本嘅香港人</span><br />\n我知日本有好多唔同嘅香港人LINE、Tg、Fb group等等，但我見過最大嘅都係得三四百人左右，而通常都係得一個地區/學校嘅人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原因主要有兩個：<br />\n- 唔同學校&amp;唔同縣嘅香港人比較少機會接觸倒對方<br />\n- 我哋尼班毒j太毒，少出去社交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因此細佬想開返個統一嘅group，方便(1)統計日本戰力、(2)有效率地推日本行動post、(3)統一日文文宣材料、(4)收集同整理資訊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (另外因爲小弟係twitter新手，所以想借大家力量幫手喺twitter打仗) <br />\n不過一樣好緊要要強調嘅係，<span style=\"color: red;\">我唔係企圖做日本大台</span>，希望大家唔好誤解我。個group係用嚟溝通，唔係用嚟俾我話事的。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">二）提供、收集&amp;整理在日行動資訊</span><br />\n尼個主要係為咗(三)儲彈藥，同埋方便大家策劃行動設計文宣等<br />\n如上面所述，其中一項為紀錄港人在日嘅行動次數、規模、地點、目的等等，主要作為日後計劃新行動時嘅參考，同俾小弟有啲數字可以撻俾記者同議員聽。<br />\n另一項為日本人為我哋做過嘅野，其中包括電視節目、新聞報導、關心香港嘅Twitter AC、日本人策劃嘅行動等，主要用途為俾小弟喺唔同媒體度可以向幫我哋嘅日本朋友道個謝、致個敬，俾返個credit人，製造好印像，同推動佢哋繼續行動。我想推廣我哋示威者好嘅形象俾日本人知！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">三）記者訪問同同議員溝通時借用名義(後面詳述)</span><br />\n由開始行動後，細佬人網特然擴闊咗好多。當中有香港史研究会嘅成員(研究港中關係嘅教授同研究香港嘅人員等)、極關心香港嘅國際關係教授、日本人twitter打手、日經嘅傳媒等。<br />\n而從我依家有嘅人網入面，我可以開始擴大規模，聯絡更多傳媒同伸手向地方議員去進一步提高日本嘅關注度。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">但問題係，以個人名義去聯絡佢哋，<br />\n(1)我唔受理、被無視嘅機率好大；<br />\n(2)對對方嚟講我嘅定位會非常糢糊，因此我講野嘅說服力好低。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以喺實際開始行動之前，我想(需要)製造一個有力嘅名義先可以做倒野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟開嘅tg group名為「在日香港人留學生」，意在代表在日嘅香港年輕人表達意見。但我都歡迎同希望唔係留學為目的而在日嘅巴絲入埋嚟，始終細佬都想統一我哋嘅溝通平台。<br />\n以以上論點為由，我希望各位可以幫我手開始擴大日本戰線規模。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求求大家幫細佬手將尼個post傳到去每一個在日真&middot;香港人手上。お願いします。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為咗香港，細佬願意犠牲安全，放線索出嚟埤你哋有需要時查我係邊個。你哋又願意入個group借我一擘之力嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下為Tg group link，希望各位在日香港人可以入嚟參加日本戰線。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/OL9UoRQEWeAPCGPZmZg_IA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOL9UoRQEWeAPCGPZmZg_IA&d=o%2BN67aGUGKsADGfJqajrgOr6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=d629704e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/OL9UoRQEWeAPCGPZmZg_IA</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b160e5560be8dc7789502446f927e723d1fe015e","tid":1659643,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:16:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJzHzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJzHzo.jpg&h=eb217258&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3c34e1034181c6d0eefa135933c3799e02082a68","tid":1659643,"uid":304288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:18:22.000Z","msg":"自推5下<br />\n1/5"},{"pid":"98f89a3c14d7a75a69db687b4e5dfadd08dc14d9","tid":1659643,"uid":304288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:29:59.000Z","msg":"2/5"},{"pid":"b8243f860c03b3b5c2ec25898676bcd84c2a1f89","tid":1659643,"uid":304288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:31:01.000Z","msg":"3/5"},{"pid":"c6d4862b8f1399eb90d152e7eb901bcb48c86e7c","tid":1659643,"uid":304288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:36:49.000Z","msg":"4/5"},{"pid":"ea21576d01a1f13bd43dc158fab777d0c05ea92c","tid":1659643,"uid":304288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:38:13.000Z","msg":"5/5"},{"pid":"ab622f93c8c813f664b16368d716aa3b15adb2c3","tid":1659643,"uid":12455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:47:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d08c898ee435646056b7badb7c1c15a7b224894","tid":1659643,"uid":134840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:49:13.000Z","msg":"幫你推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e0030a59f8f793bc0e622932593fa75bb8d1e4","tid":1659643,"uid":119072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:57:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91b04b960555ef780c7f8e234332593352fc9cdc","tid":1659643,"uid":126198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:58:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"644d0636d0a5208a02d72f2bb2fb273f03480561","tid":1659643,"uid":25183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:37:40.000Z","msg":"幫你推一推"},{"pid":"0cc1c73afb8bfcecf56b68172724070b033bf827","tid":1659643,"uid":30